ncmpc|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
ncmpc: ncmpc (A curses client for the Music Player Daemon)
ncmpc:
ncmpc: ncmpc is a curses client for the Music Player Daemon (MPD). ncmpc
ncmpc: connects to a MPD running on a machine on the local network, and
ncmpc: controls this with an interface inspired by cplay. 
ncmpc:
ncmpc: http://www.musicpd.org/clients/ncmpc/
ncmpc:
ncmpc:
ncmpc: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
ncmpc:
